Multiplatforme TV Guide that enables program recording and playing. GUI a la Windows Media Center. Sourcing XMLTV data and targetting VLC player. To be used with a remote controller.

A port of tv-rec-play (ActionScript) to Java 7.
Targetting a 1-second launch even with an XML tv guide for several days and over 50 channels.
Using a SAX parsing approach.


You can reuse and adapt it according to GPL v3 license.

Stephane Coutant, http://scoutant.org

